      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775743434814,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Starting with iteration circled in green in the last step. \n\nAttempt #1: Tried decreasing learning rate to 5e-4, epochs at 1000,\nand hidden size down to 32. This worsened model performance.\n\nAttempt #2: Went back to model configurations circled in green in last\nstep but included two LSTM layers, this made the loss much worse\nwith clear signs of overfitting.  ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Starting with iteration circled in green in the last step. \n\nAttempt #1: Tried decreasing learning rate to 5e-4, epochs at 1000, and hidden size down to 32. This worsened model performance.\n\nAttempt #2: Went back to model configurations circled in green in last step but included two LSTM layers, this made the loss much worse with clear signs of overfitting.  ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
